<-!------------------------------ 4.1 ------------------------------!->

Additions
    [+] Added ESLint and Prettier for code quality and consistency.
    [+] Implemented a database system using better-sqlite3 to remember active channels.
    [+] The bot will now automatically rejoin its last active channel on startup.
    [+] Added a `data` directory for database storage.

Changes
    [*] Updated all outdated npm dependencies to their latest versions.
    [*] Refactored configuration from `config.json` to a more secure `.env` file.
    [*] Centralized all audio player logic into a new `utils/player.js` module for better maintainability.
    [*] Improved the logger to only write error stacks to a log file.

Fixes
    [!] Cleaned up console logs for a quieter startup process.
